title: How to Install an AEM Air Intake on a 2015 Subaru WRX 2.0L
description: Add horsepower and torque by following these straightforward steps to install an AEM Air Intake (part # AEM 21-732C).

asset.title: 2015 Subaru WRX 2.0L AEM Air Intake Installation
asset.description:
AEM 21-732C performance air induction system was designed for the 2015 Subaru WRX with a 2.0L engine. 

http://www.aemintakes.com/search/product.aspx?prod=21-732C

This air intake includes a vehicle specific tube, a high-flow performance AEM Dryflow® air filter, and other hardware needed for installation and easy to follow step-by-step instructions.
asset.author: KNfilters
